name: Team Mate: Sell Space
description:
Sell Space is an incremental game where you click a planet to sell land/space. Over time as you gather and sell more land you will notice the object orbiting around the Earth will change. The goal is to get over 1000 money to summon the blackhole.  However there is a catch random meteorites might fall and destroy some of your land causing you to lose money.  The meteorites falling only increase the more land you sell.  Can you get rich quick?

You play as an entrepreneur who is looking to make it big selling land in space. 

As the saying goes "It's free real estate".
